          fields:
            - type: "h2"
              text: "Helping The People Of Ottawa Around The House!"
            - type: "p"
              text: "Hughes Home Services began with Wendall Hughes’ early experience working alongside his father in the family’s contracting business. With over 30 years of experience, Wendall and his team provide trusted Ottawa home repair and handyman services. We approach each project with care and focus on delivering results that make our clients happy."
